# Design Tokens & Component System

## Colors
- Primary: #5A8FB0
- Ink: #1A1A1A
- Ink Muted: #6B6B6B
- Surface Background: #FCFAF3
- Card Background: #FFFFFF
- Border: #EFE9D8
- Priority High: #C76A55
- Priority Medium: #C9A23A
- Priority Low / Success: #7A9165

## Typography
- Display: 28px Bold, Line Height 36px, Tracking -0.5px
- H1: 22px SemiBold, Line Height 28px, Tracking -0.2px
- H2: 18px SemiBold, Line Height 24px, Tracking 0px
- Body: 16px Regular, Line Height 24px, Tracking 0px
- Caption: 14px Medium, Line Height 20px, Tracking 0px
- Small: 12px Medium, Line Height 16px, Tracking +0.1px

## Spacing System
- Base unit: 4px | Available steps: 4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48

## Corner Radius
- Small: 8px (Chips, Checkboxes)
- Card: 12px (Task Cards, Stats Cards, Modals)
- Button: 16px (Primary Buttons, Form Inputs)
- Pill/Avatar: 9999px (Fully Rounded Avatars, Selection States)

## Global Constraints
- Canvas Size: 390px × 844px (iPhone 14/15 Form Factor)
- Safe Area Margins: Left 16px, Right 16px, Top 48px, Bottom 32px
- Base Elevation: Soft Shadow `0px 4px 12px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.04)`

